<div class="row margin-below border-top--mild">
	<div class="col-sm-12 margin-above">
		<h3 class="margin-below--none">Answer the questions below
			<span class="hint display-block">You will have the opportunity to tell us more in the text box below.</span>
		</h3>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row margin-below">
	<div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-5">
		<legend class="legend-label legend-label--light">Have your duties or responsibilities changed as a result of your condition?
